        <item>
            <title>1.8.0</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Apr 2026 11:38:40 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>28</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.8.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features
- **Syntax highlighting** — Code blocks now have Prism.js-powered syntax highlighting matching Claude Desktop's color scheme (26 languages supported)
- **Code block styling** — Code blocks have proper border, background, and padding matching Claude Desktop exactly

### Changes
- Custom CSS (canopy-overrides.css) extracted to external file for easier editing and faster iteration
- DOM globals (`document`, `window`, `console`, etc.) are recognized and colored as known classes
- Syntax highlighter uses debounced MutationObserver for smooth streaming without DOM thrash
]]></description>
