        <item>
            <title>1.7.0</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 08 Apr 2026 14:03:11 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>27</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.7.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features
- Redesigned launcher with side-by-side two-column layout: Recents (directories) on the left, Sessions on the right
- Added "Continue session" checkbox that automatically resumes the most recent session when launching from a directory
- Session options (model, effort, permission) are now visible in both local and SSH remote modes

### Changes
- Updated launcher styling with material backgrounds, fixed-height scrollable lists, and dividers
- Compact header with smaller icon and cleaner typography
- Wider layout (720pt) with improved spacing
- Session timestamps now show absolute date/time instead of relative time
- Recent directory rows show selected state highlight and hover-to-remove button
]]></description>
